(A) Evidence of Erosion: Siltation caused by Parkland Poultry farm by removing old culverts. Was convicted of offence and clean-up was carried out.
(B) Particulars of Scouring: Parkland Poultry was convicted of silting the creek, caused by unathorized removal of old culverting. Repair was carried out.
(C) Water levels: Normal flows in November. Low in October.
(D) Spawning distribution: Coho spawn above Blythwood culvert. Chum spawn evenly below Blythwood culvert.
